Description: Saudi Industrial Export (known as: SIECO) is a public company, listed on Saudi Stock Exchange “Tadawul” (TDWL) since November 1995. SIECO operates within the Capital Goods sector focusing on Trading Companies and Distributors. It has subsidiary operating across Saudi Arabia, working on Construction Materials. SIECO is based in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia and was established in June 1990.
